    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Make a melee attack against the target, dealing damage as normal, except half the damage becomes wind damage as a tiger of wind rips the target to shreds. You can deal 3d6 damage to yourself to improve the attack's damage by 2d6 wind damage (Reflex negates).</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra and 1 HP to increase the damage of the attack by 1d6, up to 1d6 per level or 8d6 total.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step allows you to take no dam- age when creating a more powerful attack. The fifth step allows you to ignore the damage you would take when empowering this technique.</p>\n",
